166Ôćĺ/**
167Ôćĺ * Get the filtered evaluator count based on evaluatorFilter
168Ôćĺ * This mirrors the backend logic in src/shared/evaluation/evaluator-types.ts
169Ôćĺ * - "all": 17 evaluators total
170Ôćĺ * - "errors": 13 error evaluators (01-10, 13, 17, 19)
171Ôćĺ * - "suggestions": 4 suggestion evaluators (11, 12, 14, 15)
